summary: I previously worked as a secondary school English teacher, in Amsterdam. After relocating to the UK, I am using my bilingual language skills and experience in different ways. This includes teaching English - EFL and Business English - teaching Dutch as a foreign language, and translation/ transcreation between these languages.
